[[Translation:en/Basesets]]

A '''base set''' is a basic set of media files used by OpenTTD for graphics and sound. OpenTTD needs at least a set of base graphics to work at all. Music and sounds are optional.

These are the official OpenTTD base sets:

* [[en/Basesets/OpenGFX]]: Base graphics
* [[en/Basesets/OpenMSX]]: Base music
* [[en/Basesets/OpenSFX]]: Base sounds